{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_01","textHome":"什么？如果想组个魔法少女好朋友@小队的话……抱歉，能去找别人吗？我啊，@已经决定无论什么时候，都只为自己使用@魔法了。在战场上碰面的话还请多指教。@赌上猎物……堂堂正正的比试吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":200}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_18","textHome":"我发现了。@玩到最后啊，乐谱都可以背下来了。@所以这个还能锻炼大脑哦。@怎么样？你也试着跳一曲吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_19","textHome":"嗯，我感觉到了，状态不错！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_20","textHome":"这种感觉，真是不错……@不如去随便干一场吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_21","textHome":"看到和我一样为了傻事而许愿的家伙@我就气不打一处来。不过……@像我一样的人……我是没法放着不管的啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":300}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_22","textHome":"已经许过愿的事就没法回头了。@所以我也希望……那些为了他人@而成为魔法少女的人……@能迎来幸福的结局。@那样的话，我也算是得到拯救了吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200650}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_23","textHome":"有为了他人而许愿，最后得到幸福的人……@也有为了自己而许愿……只落得悲惨下场的人……@所以……我不用去后悔那一天我许下的愿望。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":300}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_24","textHome":"哟！你终于来啦。我刚游完一轮。@不过，我还完全没游够呢，@你要来和我比一场吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200650}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_25","textHome":"夏天天亮得早，所以这个点我就已经醒了……@虽然也可以再去睡会儿……@不过机会难得，还是去游泳吧～"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_26","textHome":"提到海之家的话，@那就是炒面、拉面、咖喱饭、章鱼烧……@一个劲纠结也没用，那就一样一样开吃吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200650}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":200}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_27","textHome":"旅店的晚饭是什么呢？@虽然在海之家大吃了一顿，@不过海鲜还能照吃不误。@晚饭是海鲜对吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_03","textHome":"越是单纯的人……@是不是就越容易受伤啊……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_28","textHome":"因为要放烟花，所以我带来了烤玉米。@吃倒是还没有吃，@但是不是有烟花大会的气氛了？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200650}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_29","textHome":"就和你看到的一样，@吃好了喝好了，也应该休息好才对。@虽然我嘴上说着没问题，@实际上她们真的好吵啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":300}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_30","textHome":"这么热的天气真是难受啊。@但魔女是不会感到天气热的吧。@算了，只要能掉悲叹之种，@辛苦就辛苦些吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_31","textHome":"我穿着泳装的话，对方会不会也穿着呢……@我倒是觉得不用那么完美地还原，@不过这地方倒是很守原则啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":300}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_32","textHome":"要是因为是夏天就掉以轻心的话，@可是会受伤的哦。@不管做什么事，都要拿出相应的觉悟来哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":200}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_33","textHome":"我就稍微尝个味道而已，@沙耶香就在旁边吵个不停。@没办法，我的刨冰也给她吃一口吧。@苹果味的，你也要吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_34","textHome":"我是吃流水素面的专家哦。@流水的装置就交给像麻美那样的@喜欢多管闲事的家伙吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_35","textHome":"现在不是赶海的时候吗？@我想试试吃自己采的贝类……@但没到时候的话就没办法了啊……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200650}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_36","textHome":"长泳比赛吗！可以！@事先说好了，关系到胜负的事，我不会输的。@我要一口气游到终点！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":200}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_37","textHome":"我觉得泳装什么样的都行，@但麻美她吵着说机会难得，要去买新的。@虽然我也很喜欢新泳装就是了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_04","textHome":"不知道已经多久……@没有在这么时髦的饭店里吃饭了啊？@真好吃。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_38","textHome":"焰那样的泳装不怎么适合我，@我也并不打算去穿，但总是忍不住去看，@是因为那个一直飘来飘去的东西吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_39","textHome":"嗯——啊！我懂了！@感觉沙耶香的泳装，好像很适合什么运动，@想起来是冲浪！很适合对吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200650}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200650}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_40","textHome":"夏天在海边，穿着泳装游泳，@吃着各种东西，放着烟花……@连我自己都觉得太松懈了，但是真的很开心。@真的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_060.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_50_41","textHome":"噫呀啊啊啊！？好冷！！@是谁！刚刚在我身后泼水的家伙是谁！@干了这种事就做好被回击的觉悟吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":200}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_42","textHome":"那么就放手大干一场吧！"}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_43","textHome":"这场胜利归我了。"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_44","textHome":"战果很不错！"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_45","textHome":"好啦，要吃什么呢——"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200650}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_46","textHome":"打败敌人了！"}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_63","textHome":"交给我吧！这里就由我来解决！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":200}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_05","textHome":"竟然送我花……呵呵。@我真是遇到了可爱的魔女啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_64","textHome":"就用这招结束这场战斗……！"}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_65","textHome":"别在我眼前跳来跳去了，蠢货！"}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_66","textHome":"就用这招让你闭嘴……！盟神抉枪!!@哈啊啊啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":200}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_02","textHome":"我是佐仓杏子，幸会。@想和我一起战斗的话，就请我吃顿晚饭吧？@……开个玩笑。午饭就可以啦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":200650,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200650}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_13","textHome":"嗯，感觉还算不错。就这样继续吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":100}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_14","textHome":"好！到了这一步，@就该考虑下个阶段该怎么办了，对吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":100}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_15","textHome":"每个人都有不同的故事……@那么，这就是我的故事。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200650}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":200}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_16","textHome":"我的性格就是要做就要做到最好。@就算是最高难度我也要完美通关。@哈？当然是在说跳舞机啦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp.json","id":200650}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":100}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200650,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2006_00_17","textHome":"因为要追上不断从上面掉下来的音符，@所以我的动态视力也得到了锻炼，@对战斗也会有帮助哦。@嗯，说的就是跳舞机。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200650,"motion":100}]}]},"version":3}